Reasoning: The paper discusses the reduction of various function problems on Boolean formulas to a generic problem of computing a minimal set subject to a monotone predicate. This involves algorithmic techniques and optimization strategies, which are typically studied in the areas of artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), logic in computer science (cs.LO), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), and computational complexity (cs.CC).
